    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and its signature 8,400 RPM redline. This platform utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed manual gearbox to deliver a visceral, linear power band. The M-Variable differential lock remains sharp, providing excellent torque distribution across the rear axle. Recent technical service includes proactive rod bearing replacement and refreshed throttle actuators, addressing the common failure points of this high-strung valvetrain. The suspension retains its factory Electronic Damper Control (EDC) functionality, paired with a rigid subframe for precise turn-in. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with use, the powertrain and drivetrain integrity remain exceptional for the spirited driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
