    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the sought-after 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via a calibrated limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including documented subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The chassis remains taut with refreshed control arm bushings and factory-spec dampening, ensuring the signature E46 handling profile. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain and longitudinal dynamics remain exceptionally sharp for the discerning driver.",
